# Worktree feature banner

The App header feature blurb under the title (`p.tagline.feature-boost-note` in `src/App.tsx`) must describe the **current worktree/branch purpose in one line**.

- When creating or changing an explore worktree/spike, **always update that string** in that worktree’s `App.tsx`. Do not leave stale copy such as “Feature boost: FF-style camera-facing faces + chunkier weapons…”.
- When spinning up a new explore worktree for testing, set the blurb as part of setup so the header matches the spike under test.
